    {
      "body": "Poppy Beifong was ${link_0}'s mother and a ${link_1} in ${link_2}. Like her ${link_3}, Poppy cared deeply for her daughter, but was extremely protective of her, unwilling to acknowledge the young ${link_4}'s capabilities.",
